ForwardAgent      yes
ForwardX11Trusted yes
ForwardX11Timeout 8h
HashKnownHosts    no
Compression       yes
Ciphers           aes128-ctr
ServerAliveInterval 30

Host samsara.ext
    HostName samsara
    ForwardX11 yes
    ProxyCommand ssh -q styx.obspm.fr nc -q0 -w 90 samsara 22

Host samsara.tun
    ForwardX11 yes
    ProxyCommand ssh -q styx.obspm.fr nc -q0 -w 90 samsara 22
    LocalForward 1502 samsara.obspm.fr:1502

Host github.com
    ForwardX11 no

Host *
    ForwardX11 yes